snippet.title: Amber Heard vs Johnny Depp: Part 1 - TRH 116
snippet.description:
The Rabbit Hole 116
Amber Heard vs Johnny Depp: Part 1 

Part 1 of the infamous recorded fight between Amber Heard & Johnny Depp

The Rabbit Hole Opinion:
It appears that things got way out of hand & there doesn't seem to be any real winners. 

What Do You Think? 
Who is right? or are they both wrong?
